<br />
JP Hauge on Manchester United&rsquo;s scouts watching him: &ldquo;It was not my best game today, unfortunately, so that&rsquo;s a bit disappointing. Let&rsquo;s hope he liked what he (Tommy M&oslash;ller Nielsen) saw though.&rdquo;

